thread.title_full: Metropolitan Movers reviewed by Paul Marker

author: Paul Marker
title: Paul Marker
text: I found the service met my expectations and I received two Quote: s within days of making contact. Unfortunately I never heard from the third company. I would have no hesitation in recommending this service to anyone wanting to find a good reputable moving company.
